Season 1, Episode 3 - Air Date: 10/26/07

In the third preliminary round of America's Psychic Challenge, four new psychics were put to the test: Tori Allah, Catherine Powell, Joseph Tittel, and Michelle Whitedove.

In the three different challenges, the psychics had to find a man in the trunk of his car in a full parking-lot, match the bride with her groom, and recount the details of a woman's death at the hands of her husband's hitman.
